{"tid":396420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陶傑：請全港醫院即時中止中文大學醫學院實習醫生合約","createTime":"2017-09-11T15:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T05:52:39.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1141,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e41622a9cdf8034e7ab894126d4c2318fc274ecc","tid":396420,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:48:36.000Z","msg":"【請全港醫院即時中止中大醫學院實習醫生合約】<br />\n<br />\n中大醫學院副教授許金山涉嫌謀殺妻女被捕，將轉介高等法院，其間還押懲教署看管。<br />\n<br />\n天地有正氣，哈哈，不如全港醫院、醫務所、病人，一齊杯葛抵制中大醫學院學生？亦請認明你將來二十年看的醫生，一定不可以出自中大？<br />\n<br />\n轉自陶傑 Channel Facebook 專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1637896806282836&amp;id=272574169481780\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1637896806282836%26id%3D272574169481780&d=vUg23RdbbGWRY1NFBUUeLm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d3e298fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1637896806282836&amp;id=272574169481780</a>"},{"pid":"af53f8d1264369140072fe63c72667577533de9d","tid":396420,"uid":16528,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019039ccb6ac7765c0f75be006d9858a9b97dbc8","tid":396420,"uid":122601,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"抽水抽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d452e0a08f33cd6eb5e1477f7815fba9a0f00bfd","tid":396420,"uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eccb156ce94a96911a206cccab63d2a2f77c7c2","tid":396420,"uid":135445,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"靚抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f038c257043065bb6d32df9a3c16d400420d74ac","tid":396420,"uid":22736,"like":5